{
  "stem": "14156.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Any-- I don't recall right away, OK.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They played music, and you had to go by.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then one of the SS used to say, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That means you take your hat off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's like saluting, so to speak of.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then you kept on walking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And once you pass the stand, the viewing stand, with the band, then [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then you kept on walking into the factory, into the place where we were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And many times, on the way down there, there was-- there was guards on either side, naturally.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if they wanted to kill someone, they took the cap away from this person, from the prisoner, and threw it in the field.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then the guard said, go!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Get it!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was death.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They wanted you to get out of the-- out of the-- the-- the-- the surrounding of the-- of the-- of the guards.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then you were like you want to run away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They had a reason.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then they killed them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then they screamed, down!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Everybody on the floor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the poor guy was running, and they shot him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Happened many times.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Factory.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave me a job drilling holes in the wire boxes-- boxes, electrical, the wire boxes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had four or five openings where they put steel pipes in and then ran the wires, the electrical wire, through, in order to-- to, you know, get the electrical thing going, with lights and everything.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then, once I had-- there was a lot of Polish people there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were not so kosher, I would say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Poles, I'm sorry, but they were always a little bit anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a fellow, a young guy, you know, who always looked at us, or looked at me.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
